    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.HU4lNUAme2XmxfAN]{Weapon Group: Small Arms, One-Handed}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The almost inaudible wave-rifle discharge inflicts massive damage on physical targets and on enemy combat units. However, in one incident, a test group encoun</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">tered undead opponents and reported a much-elevated damage potential. Undead creatures are vulnerable to hits from this weapon.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 62px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Disruptor </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 46px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">45,000 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 75px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1d8 radiant </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 49px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">50/200 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 44px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">10 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 108px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000;\">AP, </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">reload (20-H)</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.iK2nOll8s5dIVgVp]{AP (Armor Piercing)}</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.QjoW3JNAsq3eJt4s]{Reload 20-M} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.lmAMoPPYbIwgHfGl]{Battry Cell, Medium}</p>",
